As of the census<ref name=census2010/> of 2010, there were 83 people living in the CDP. There were 109 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] of the CDP was 97.6% White, 1.2% from some other race, and 1.2% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 4.8% of the population.

